<h3>Key Features</h3>
<p>This template provides flexible support for various sensor types, with the ability to swap in almost any analog sensor. Its modular setup makes it simple to adapt to different sensor configurations, offering a robust display platform for multiple types of data.</p>
<ul>
  <li>Supports a wide range of analog sensors, including temperature, humidity, and moisture sensors.</li>
  <li>Digital sensor compatibility is in progress, ensuring broader sensor support in future versions.</li>
</ul>

